item.title: Newbienewty's HighAlcher
item.dc:creator: @hey321 hey321
item.description:
@hey321 wrote:

Nice, i remade it a bit for you, but good job.

Here’s the remade version:

[php]
//------------------> Made by Newbienewty
//-----------------> Setup is very ovbious!

program NewbienewtysHighAlcher;
{.include SRL/SRL.scar}
{.include SRL/SRL/skill/magic.scar}
Const
TotalNeeded = 128;
GoldPerItem = 1234; //Gold Per Item
item = ‘Item Alching Here’; //Item Name(For Report)
InvNumber = 20; //Amount In Inventory You want Alched

var
TotalDone : Integer;

Procedure ChangeReport;
begin
cleardebug;
TotalDone:= TotalDone + 1;
writeln(‘High Alched’ + inttostr(TotalDone) + ‘’ + (Item));
Writeln(‘Made’ + inttostr(totalDone*GoldPerItem) + ’ times left’);
end;

Procedure HighAlch;
begin
Gametab(7);
fixmage(true);
castspell(31)
MouseItem(InvNumber, true)
Wait(Random(23)+2400);
ChangeReport;
end;

begin
SetupSRL;
Repeat
HighAlch;
Until(TotalDone = TotalNeeded);
FTWait(60000)
end.
[/php]
